{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-gradual-css-linear-gradient","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Napravite postepen CSS `linear-gradient()`","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Postavljanje boje na HTML elemente nije ograničeno samo na jednu solidnu boju. CSS pruža mogućnost korišćenja prelaza boja, poznatih i kao gradienti, na elementima. Ovo se postiže kroz <code>background</code> svojstvo i <code>linear-gradient()</code> funkciju. Evo opšte sintakse:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">background: linear-gradient(gradient_direction, color 1, color 2, color 3, ...);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Prvi argument definiše smer prelaza odakle počinje - može biti definisan u stepenima, gde <code>90deg</code> kreira vertikalni prelaz (sa leva na desno) i <code>45deg</code> kreira dijagonalni prelaz (od dole levo ka gore desno). Sledeći argumenti definišu redosled boja koje se koriste u prelazu.</p>\n<p>Primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">background: linear-gradient(90deg, red, yellow, rgb(204, 204, 255));\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d78a5367417b2b2512ad6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristite <code>linear-gradient()</code> za <code>background</code> svojstvo <code>div</code> elementa, sa smerom od 35 stepeni da promenite boju od <code>#CCFFFF</code> do <code>#FFCCCC</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cg4dpt9","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301047,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-gradual-css-linear-gradient"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  div {\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    width: 70%;\n    height: 400px;\n    margin: 50px auto;\n\n  }\n\n</style>\n\n<div></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>div</code> element treba da ima <code>linear-gradient</code> <code>background</code> sa navedenim smerom i bojama.</p>","testString":"const divElement = document.querySelector('div');\nconst divStyle = window.getComputedStyle(divElement); \nassert.match(divStyle?.background, /linear-gradient\\(35deg, rgb\\(204, 255, 255\\), rgb\\(255, 204, 204\\)\\)/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"create-a-gradual-css-linear-gradient","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-a-css-linear-gradient-to-create-a-striped-element","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/adjust-the-tone-of-a-color","id":"587d78a5367417b2b2512ad6","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1